# Source artifact storage policy -- see ADR 018 and docs/platform/STORAGE.md.
#
# Each line below is dormant LFS plumbing. The matching `.gitignore` block
# prevents source files from ever being staged today; if/when the policy
# flips to real LFS storage, removing the gitignore line activates the
# filter automatically. Bytes live in $AIRBOSS_HANDBOOK_CACHE today
# (default ~/Documents/airboss-handbook-cache/), not the repo.
#
# Add a new line below for each new content corpus.

handbooks/**/*.pdf filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
regulations/cfr-*/**/*.xml filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
